      "body" : "I&#39;m not convinced that preventing NPEs is a good thing.  An NPE means you should have a <code>null</code> in <code>s</code>.  It is a sign of a bug, not something that should be hidden.  Dealing with a <code>null</code> is not part of the OP&#39;s stated requirements."
